</p>
<p>
Eolytha the <a class="nonexistent" href="./RohanKnight">RohanKnight</a> Haftedmaster (Void-diver) 
<pre>a) The Mighty Hammer 'Grond' (E:27072699, L:50) (9d9) (+71,+46) [+10] (+3 attacks)
